      "id": "PopularPost318456",
      "post_content": "This card has been pretty useful for me in casual. It's not mythically awesome, but consider: it's a [Sacred Nectar](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Sacred Nectar) attached to a 3/4 vanilla. Not bad for 5CMC. Your opponent will think twice before bouncing it. If you have a way to get it back into your hand, you can up the lifegain. I have this in a deck with [Narrow Escape](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Narrow Escape), and they combo quite nicely - if it dies from combat or is removed, bounce it for 4 lifegain, cast it next turn for another 4 lifegain. That's 12 lifegain, which could easily extend your game by 1-2 turns. I like this guy.",
      "posted_by": "wideyes",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost318456\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_post\">This card has been pretty useful for me in casual. It's not mythically awesome, but consider: it's a <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Sacred Nectar\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Sacred Nectar\">Sacred Nectar</a> attached to a 3/4 vanilla. Not bad for 5CMC. Your opponent will think twice before bouncing it. If you have a way to get it back into your hand, you can up the lifegain. I have this in a deck with <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Narrow Escape\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Narrow Escape\">Narrow Escape</a>, and they combo quite nicely - if it dies from combat or is removed, bounce it for 4 lifegain, cast it next turn for another 4 lifegain. That's 12 lifegain, which could easily extend your game by 1-2 turns. I like this guy.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '318456'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy96697\">wideyes</span>\r\n                                (5/30/2013 12:29:34 AM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\